data.description: Almost new and barely lived in. This beautiful three-level townhome with fantastic features offers functionality and comfort with 2400 sq ft of modern living space!  The home features hardwood flooring throughout the central area with a floating fireplace.  A spacious, gourmet kitchen equipped with granite, stainless steel appliances, a five-burner stove, 42-inch gourmet cabinets, and a built-in microwave. A large island in the kitchen is perfect for meal preparation and gatherings. The dining area and living area offer natural lighting and plenty of space.  The lower level has a half bath and a generously sized recreation room, providing additional space for entertainment or relaxation. You will find the owner's suite, two additional bedrooms, and the laundry area on the upper level. The spacious and luxurious owners' suite features a large walk-in closet. The owner's bathroom has double sinks, offering ample countertop space with a shower designed for two.  Location is key, and this property has it all! Commuting becomes a breeze just minutes from the Greenbelt Metro, making this home an excellent choice for those seeking accessibility and convenience. Schedule a tour today. Please follow COVID guidelines. Schedule online with showing time.
